snippet.title: Pokemon Final Legacy - F3 2019 Trailer
snippet.description:
Originally From F3 2019 - https://youtu.be/0htUp3MoBjA
This Fan Project has been cancelled. 

Original Description:
Pokémon Final Legacy is my secret project I been working on for about a year now where Professor Oak dies...

Pokémon Final Legacy features 2 versions, a Offline and Online Version. Offline will be available at launch while Online will be TBD at a later date. 

For Updates and To Hangout, Check out the discord -
